title: Daylight sighting by a hunter on her hunting property near Pembine
observed: My mom seen a creature she could not explain on our hunting property it was crouched over. She said it turned to look at her and she knew it was no bear she called me right away to come look and when I looked at the spot it was it looked like something had covered tracks.
location_details: Route 141 North into Marinette county, to Pembine, Wisconsin.
